    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK492">
<l>muraṇcērnta moympi ṉavarkku maraṇcērntā</l>
<l>mākkam palavun tarum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even to those who are men of power and expedients, an attack in connection with a fortification will yield many advantages.</l>
